 </row>
 <row>
   <entry><emphasis>Step 4. Translate</emphasis>.</entry>
   <entry/>
 </row>

 <row>
   <entry>Write the appropriate formula.</entry>
   <entry><media id="eip-id1167261299729" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_03_04_024b_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
 </row>
 <row>
   <entry>Substitute.</entry>
   <entry><media id="eip-id1167265968146" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_03_04_024c_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
