 <row>
   <entry><emphasis>Step 6. Check. </emphasis><newline/><newline/><m:math><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:mi>P</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>≟</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mn>104</m:mn></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>≟</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mn>104</m:mn></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:mn>104</m:mn></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mn>104</m:mn><m:mo>✓</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:math></entry><entry/>
 </row>
  <row>
   <entry> <emphasis>Step 7. Answer </emphasis>the question.</entry>
   <entry>The perimeter of the rectangle is 104 meters.</entry>
