<title>Practice Makes Perfect</title>
<para id="fs-id1168345418382"><emphasis effect="bold">Solving Applications Using Triangle Properties</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-id1166423882755">In the following exercises, solve using triangle properties.</para>
<exercise id="fs-id1168345459370">
